; Force file-based voicemail instead of ODBC voicemail
; FreePBX loads app_voicemail_odbc.so by default, which requires
; database tables that are never set up. This ensures the standard
; file-based app_voicemail.so is used instead.
noload => app_voicemail_odbc.so
noload => app_voicemail_imap.so
load => app_voicemail.so
